snippet.textDisplay:
If you're a kid that grew up with 90s Saturday cartoons you might know who this character is. It seems Sony is trying to re-introduce a line of villains/anti-heroes from the Spiderman universe. At first I thought it was Man-Bat from DC, but since its Morbius from Marvel, now who shall he be pitted against? And why is it not Dracula organ theme for the trailer?

Morbius is an anti-hero "vampire" that appears in the Spiderman universe. He sometimes cross-paths with Spiderman and Blade the Vampire Hunter. But he also helped in the effort to reverse the transformation of Spiderman to Man-Spider.
snippet.textOriginal:
